earch report</span><span style="font-family:'Arial (W1)'; font-size:9pt; font-style:italic">. </span></p><p style="margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:'Arial (W1)'; font-size:9pt">(</span><span style="font-family:'Arial (W1)'; font-size:9pt">This report has been submitted for publication and we will be able to supply th</span><span style="font-family:'Arial (W1)'; font-size:9pt">e committee with a copy shortly.</span><span style="font-family:'Arial (W1)'; font-size:9pt">)</span></p><p style="margin:0pt"><a name="_ftn8"></a><a href="#_ftnref8">[8]</a><span style="font-family:'Arial (W1)'; font-size:9pt"> One </span><span style="font-family:'Arial (W1)'; font-size:9pt">was ‘</span><span style="font-family:'Arial (W1)'; font-size:9pt">Other type of employee</span><span style="font-family:'Arial (W1)'; font-size:9pt">’.</span></p><p style="margin:0pt"><a name="_ftn9"></a><a href="#_ftnref9">[9]</a><span style="font-family:'Arial (W1)'; font-size:9pt"> </span><span style="font-family:'Arial (W1)'; font-size:9pt">http://www.esrc.ac.uk/_images/career-choices-and-impact-on-graduates-report_tcm8-6388.pdf</span><span style="font-family:'Arial (W1)'; font-size:9pt"> </span></p><p style="margin:0pt"><a name="_ftn10"></a><a href="#_ftnref10">[10]</a><span style="font-family:'Arial (W1)'; font-size:9pt"> </span><span style="font-family:'Arial (W1)'; font-size:9pt">http://www.bis.gov.uk/assets/cst/docs/files/whats-new/10-584-vision-uk-research.pdf</span></p><p style="margin:0pt"><a name="_ftn11"></a><a href="#_ftnref11">[11]</a><span style="font-family:'Arial (W1)'; font-size:9pt"> </span><span style="font-family:'Arial (W1)'; font-size:9pt">http://wellc.me/15av5kF</span><span style="font-family:'Arial (W1)'; font-size:9pt"> </span></p><p style="margin:0pt"><a name="_ftn12"></a><a href="#_ftnref12">[12]</a><span style="font-family:'Arial (W1)'; font-size:9pt"> </span><span style="font-family:'Arial (W1)'; font-size:9pt">http://wellc.me/17q0ipG</span><span style="font-family:'Aria